    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Amusurgus (Amusurgus) caerulus sp. nov. male holotype when alive in dorsal (A), lateral (B) and ventral (C) views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5886482/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5886486>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Amusurgus (Amusurgus) caerulus sp. nov. female paratype when alive in dorsal (A), lateral (B) and ventral (C) views." ;
